{"tid":40420,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"喺starbucks坐，見到一堆人生贏家","createTime":"2016-12-15T07:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T18:15:06.000Z","uid":35324,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38d11672f6a888590fa9c5e0b379896a81f01e6c","tid":40420,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"見呢間starbucks平時都冇人，買左杯野飲坐喺度趕assignment deadline<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知3點半一到，突然一堆此起彼落嘅笑聲慢慢傳嚟，越嚟越大聲。<br />\n原來係一堆國際學校嘅細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲細路個個都有錢自己買野飲，仲有一兩個工人跟住喺後面。成間starbucks就咁充斥住來自年輕洋腸的雞腸同埋叫聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一個而家買杯starbucks都覺得肉赤嘅18歲毒撚，回想起我小學嘅時候一個星期可能得5蚊零用錢，不禁悲從中來。<br />\n<br />\n睇番份英文assignment，就好似佢地口中嘅急口令雞腸一樣，搞到我一頭霧水。只好仰天長嘯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a88583800a4a7683cc510d225545600e2aed15d","tid":40420,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"咩區？"},{"pid":"9d971834eaf18cdf0c9ed9b0a02f3110b93c9d10","tid":40420,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩區？</blockquote><br />\n想一齊嚟感受下自己同人生贏家嘅對比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdec8c579f0cd5fce3ba52092cfc7dde376b418","tid":40420,"uid":46469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"仰天長嘯因住嘈親人呀"},{"pid":"459dc065ffbed3b1401b9e361f9a91dd3685b8e9","tid":40420,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩區？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估又一城"},{"pid":"f3f7b3d33a3b072a5260a973b4ff850474f7d530","tid":40420,"uid":24614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:49:39.000Z","msg":"巴打 呢個世界無公平呢樣野"},{"pid":"247237d9c7f0be76d5ae80ca4fecd7e0abc56