By":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d1d3fa0417c28a055c794d3c01d5037ceb7165","tid":40420,"uid":2167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"番學校做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682c3e6b8833873cfb39062303f52ed600f19e35","tid":40420,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"九龍灣。。。太空人/cccu?"},{"pid":"4e62df55696f03a900271d40750766a9a3c2e620","tid":40420,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小朋友，命運講到尾都係要靠自己掌握嘅&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n你話制度唔公平，你一早輸喺起跑線&hellip;咁你咪諗下有無辦法，甚至去挑戰個制度囉！環顧唔同嘅時代，總有人係靠自己努力而成功嘅&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n與其坐喺度慨嘆，人哋先天贏咗你咁多，不如諗下點樣去同人爭啦！<br />\n<br />\n人生先啱啱開始啫，如果你依家就放棄，比賽就已經完結啦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nSorry 認真咗</blockquote><br />\n我都認真覆你<br />\n<br />\n屋企人本身都係冇點讀書，由細到大都冇人叫我溫多啲書，我自己又懶，亦冇話真係想進入個上流社會，一hea就hea左18年，仲未知u grad之後可以番咩工。<br />\n<br />\n我英文睇多幾隻字就有唔識，相反人地細細個已經成個環境都係英文，屋企又有錢供佢地讀好學校，搵老師幫佢地補習、學野，人地可能小學、初中已經鋼琴演奏級，而我連學琴嘅錢都比唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc455c7f7fe325c3010fb5d89639661fe9f29e67","tid":40420,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到樓主講零用錢令我唸起一段往事 -)<br />\n<br />\n以前細個一蚊零用錢都無<br />\n想買薯片之類既零食都永遠唔會有錢 <br />\n每日小息剩係企係度望住人地大大啖食我就大大啖吞口水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得有次新年老母比左個5蚊銀我話係新年禮物<br />\n當時開心都飛起因爲終於有第一次既零用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知就係開心過龍攞唔穩個5蚊銀<br />\n一下就跌左落地仲碌左入個坑渠度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喊左成日仲要比我老母閙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都有差唔多嘅經歷<br />\n細個知道屋企冇乜錢，如果有禮物收，就會好滾動好珍惜樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比起份禮物，更加珍惜父母嘅心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3212375334f4708517123dc742128ef175f6566c","tid":40420,"uid":7081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:49:06.000Z","msg":"我咁多年都冇買過Starbucks 飲，因為真係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096634b519c8bded8199c16d6ef37f791b08d047","tid":40420,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"公平咩？"},{"pid":"c02bbf4070fdbea1143844d4232cf75ea97acdde","tid":40420,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"屌嗰時我去做補習<br />\n有個International School大約中二到<br />\n話要飛去邊度練曲棍球<br />\n平時講嘢用英文，講到辣辣聲<br />\n香港人直頭好似唔識中文咁"},{"pid":"b40c037c23fccdfa1f011fc6dbd55f205fa678dd","tid":40420,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌嗰時我去做補習<br />\n有個International School大約中二到<br />\n話要飛去邊度練曲棍球<br />\n平時講嘢用英文，講到辣辣聲<br />\n香港人直頭好似唔識中文咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大埔區"},{"pid":"ca7e214ee40f821fb5d353d32b035dc8e6f5b12b","tid":40420,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"你都叫有錢買，我仲飲緊雀巢3合1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb0b285d0fdc9bfdbce47d722232b156576620b","tid":40420,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:55:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌嗰時我去做補習<br />\n有個International School大約中二到<br />\n話要飛去邊度練曲棍球<br />\n平時講嘢用英文，講到辣辣聲<br />\n香港人直頭好似唔識中文咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大埔區</blockquote><br />\n巴打你好似係hku? <br />\n你有料幫佢補習都勁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da40489f9c70e911a07f54